# FavoritesRepository Learning Topics

## High-Level Categories
1. Data Synchronization
2. Offline-First Architecture
3. Coroutines & Threading
4. Error Handling
5. Data Mapping
6. Cache Management

## Android/Kotlin Concepts Used

### Architecture Patterns
- Repository Pattern
- Offline-First Design
- Data Mapping
- SSOT (Single Source of Truth)

### Concurrency
1. Coroutines
   - withContext
   - CoroutineScope
   - Dispatchers.IO
   - suspend functions

2. Threading
   - Background Operations
   - Main-Safe Code

### Data Management
1. Room Database
   - DAO Operations
   - Entity Mapping
   - Transaction Management

2. Network Operations
   - Retrofit Integration
   - Response Handling
   - Error Management

### Error Handling
1. Result Class
2. Exception Handling
3. Null Safety
4. Error Logging

## Suggested Study Order

1. Basic Concepts
   - Repository Pattern
   - Room Database
   - Retrofit Basics

2. Concurrency
   - Coroutines
   - Dispatchers
   - Background Processing

3. Data Operations
   - CRUD Operations
   - Data Mapping
   - Cache Management

4. Synchronization
   - Online/Offline Strategy
   - Data Consistency
   - Error Recovery

5. Advanced Topics
   - Transaction Management
   - Memory Management
   - Performance Optimization

## Key Technologies
- Room Database
- Retrofit
- Kotlin Coroutines
- Android Logging
- SharedPreferences

